<div class='right-side'>
<div class='text'>The capital gains tax rate should be reduced.</div>
<div class='buttons'>
<a href="#" class="debate" title="Join the Debate">5 Arguments</a>
<a href="/shares/new?q=5702&amp;t=Q&amp;w=fb" class="facebook-share" target="_blank"></a>
