<div class='argument-text'>
Raising taxes in the middle of a bad economy will only hurt make things worse. This study shows that raising it likely would not even increase net tax revenue.<br/><a href="http://www.heritage.org/research/reports/2010/03/obamas-capital-gains-tax-hike-unlikely-to-increase-revenues">http://www.heritage.org/research/reports/2010/03/obamas-capital-gains-tax-hike-unlikely-to-increase-revenues</a>
